{
  "stem": "6130.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was very unpleasant, and then when they were through, they just let us mingle there with each other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the following morning-- in fact, in some kind of trucks-- they took us close to the railway station, where there was a huge building for horses.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in my hometown, and the county in itself, had a big business in exporting-- and maybe importing too-- horses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there was a family in our hometown that became very, very rich people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They all died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what they were doing, exporting horses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think they were importing from Italy and Spain and exporting to I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's why those big stalls were-- big buildings for horses-- horses' stalls-- were built, and that's where we  were put, in the horses' stalls.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were there maybe a day or two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's when my niece's 19th birthday was celebrated, in the horse stalls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not celebrated, but was a very sad occasion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's where we were put in the wagons and taken to Auschwitz, because we didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I want to go back to my one experience in the ghetto, where my father died.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One day, a man came, and he said, well, I want to go in the house and check out the apart-- the house where we lived-- because my wife wants to know what is the arrangement.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father got very angry and said, you are not going into my house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There is no way I'll let you go in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Oh, we will have it anyhow, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Vass.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There is no way-- you go away, and we get the bakery, and we got everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
